title: #92Noon! PA is back
description: PA returns to broadcasting 92Noon on a busy Thursday show! Wild coach Dean Evason opens, followed by Vikings GM Rick Spielman, Ben Leber's weekly bit, Vikings COO Andrew Miller and more!
